    "description": "Gaurs Group Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Business Development Manager to join our dynamic team in Mumbai. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Gaurs Group Advisory Limited:\nGaurs Group Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gaurs Group Advisory Limited!",
